### **4. 25_LiveGraphPulse**  
**Description:**  
A real-time data graphing script using Matplotlib to render incoming numbers.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveGraphPulse - Real-Time Data Plotter

LiveGraphPulse is perfect for watching a live numeric stream turn into a smooth, animated line graph.

## Features
- Real-time graphing  
- Customizable window size  
- Pause/play support  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_LiveGraphPulse.git
cd 25_LiveGraphPulse
python visualize.py
